narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 111 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 111 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: The dopest class at Yale. Something you dont wanna miss out on
I would definitely recommend this class.
I loved this class!! We had wonderful and very thought provoking discussions, and Jessica is the best!!

This si a great course with the potential to be thought provoking if you choose to engage with the material. I would recommend the class to students who are willing to think and move outside of their usual pattern. Use the open space that is this course as a means to explore why you do what you do and what your body means to you.
DEFINITELY TAKE THIS CLASS!!!!! You will not regret it! The most thought provoking and fun class I have taken at Yale thus far (aka in 3 years)!

I would say the class itself is great but it is greatly effected by where they students are themselves and how much effort they put in, on a day when some students were dragging behind the whole class was effected. I would definitely recommend taking it but would reiterate that you've got to give it your all (which I consider to be a strength of the class)
